How can you fall in love when you cant even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will diewhich makes his flirty maids behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?
(Source: Funimation)

A boy moves town, a friend of his mother with a strong Kansaiben accent takes care of him.

A flawless love story of the flawed. Stuttering lady Maximilian is forced into a marriage with Sir Riftan, but he leaves on a campaign after their wedding night. 3 years later, he triumphantly returns, ready to cherish her. As life with her husband finally begins, she only has one question does she deserve this love and happiness?
(Source: Manta)
